Package: BioCal
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Biomass Based on Forest Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dr. Andre Nakhavali
Maintainer: Dr. Andre Nakhavali <nakhavali@iiasa.ac.at>
Description: This package provides tools for calculating the biomass of trees based
    on country, species, compartment, diameter, and height. The calculations use
    specific allometric equations tailored for different tree species across various
    biogeographical zones. Use four spaces when indenting paragraphs within the Description.
